,Recommended,505210,29615096,Posted: 31 January,all,dnlgjmnz,"I absolutely recommend this game, especially for the price. I got it for 66% off after crafting a badge. This game is addictive, fun, the music is great, and you have the ability to skip tracks.. go back.. pause. It's great!! This is the perfect game to get lost in. Just old fashioned challenges. No story, no silly gimmicks. There are two moves, one is called a bump that kind of teleports you a few inches away, and the other slows down time slightly. The challenge is choosing when to use the abilities as they have recharge times. This game is great to get high and play, it's got perfect pick up and play value as well as having fun trying to beat level times. Seriously for $1 you can't beat this."
