his game can also be very buggy which the devs seem to be fixing after hearing some of them so that's why there was no bugs in the negative spot. Really there is no replay value and if you are really good at this gmaes it could take you 4-6 hours or if you're bad most likely 7-9 hours. This game really doesn't hurt your wallet unless you want small fries from MacDonalds to feed your starving self so buy it and help the devs to make better games than this one and make a new creative ideas and help make better games.Game Score: 4/10 Below Average"
